relevant_findings.general: Well developed, well nourished in no acute distress
relevant_findings.heent: Normocephalic, atraumatic, extraocular movements intact, anicteric
relevant_findings.cardiovascular: Regular rate and rhythm, normal S1/S2 without murmur, rub, or gallop
relevant_findings.pulmonary: Clear to auscultation bilaterally, no wheezes, rales or rhonchi, no respiratory distress
relevant_findings.abdominal: Soft, right lower quadrant tenderness to moderate palpation, non-distended, no mass, no hernia, mild scrotal edema right greater than left without scrotal tenderness
relevant_findings.neurological: Alert and oriented to person, place, and time, no focal neurologic deficits
